    <div class="header">
        <div class="chi_left">
            <a href="#">6789Club</a>
            <div class="chi_input">
                <input name="" placeholder="请输入您需要查找的内容 …" type="text" />
                <!--头左-->
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--头右-->
    </div>
    <!--/header-->

    <div class="main">
        <div class="chi_m_top">
            <div class="fl"><img src="~/Assets/images/logo.png" height="60" width="60" /></div>
            <div class="fr">
                <h3>6789俱乐部·因趣而生</h3>
                <p>定期为有相同兴趣的人提供活动，励志做常州最好玩的俱乐部，加入6789俱乐部，我们带你吃喝玩乐玩转生活，趣味无穷。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <form action="/user/login" method="post">
            <div class="wrapper wrapper-content login-main">
                <div class="login">
                    <div class="login-p">
                        <input type="text" name="Account" placeholder="请输入账号">
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-p">
                        <input type="password" name="PassWord" placeholder="请输入密码">
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-p">
                        <p1><label for=""><a href="/user/resiger">用户注册</a></label></p1>
                        <p><label for=""><a href="#">忘记密码</a></label></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-p">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs">登录</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <!--/main-->
